  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/5c42da3395c3defa47cd1e446240d29e.poster.avif?t=1684741024\" width=738 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/5c42da3395c3defa47cd1e446240d29e.webm?t=1684741024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/5c42da3395c3defa47cd1e446240d29e.mp4?t=1684741024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Idle Gem Quest: is a clicker game set  in a fantasy world.  Slay monsters, unlock new  classes, upgrade heroes, and travel to new lands. Buy upgrades and unlock achievements to develop your team of Idle heroes.<br><br>What will you discover on your journey?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/8ea4bc32d2bedf43bbe4fc9b73453ef1.poster.avif?t=1684741024\" width=738 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/8ea4bc32d2bedf43bbe4fc9b73453ef1.webm?t=1684741024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/8ea4bc32d2bedf43bbe4fc9b73453ef1.mp4?t=1684741024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>FEATURES<br>- Scratch the itch for your next clicker game<br>- Active play increases rewards <br>- Upgrade and maximize income while idle <br>- 5 classes to manage with varied input <br>- 70+ plus characters <br>- Achievements!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144290/extras/430e7a45cbd03954607b7a27544d94b1.poster.a